text.tspan: Prevalence of anxiety disorders by age, World, 1990 to 2019
Share of population within each age category suffering from an anxiety disorder. This is measured across both sexes. Figures attempt to
provide a true estimate (going beyond reported diagnosis) of anxiety disorder prevalence based on medical, epidemiological data, surveys
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
